This project is created in order to publish events. 
Every event will have it's own task list which will help people manage their time and do not waste it on figuring out 
what should be done next. 
Here i have 4 models.
  User model one-to-one with companies. That means only one user can own a conpany at a time.
  User can have multiple events.
  
  Event can have multiple tasks and only one author.
  
  Task can have only one event.
  
  Company can have multiple events and only one author.
